title: Total vehicles entering Canada in Canada 2017
summary: The Number of Total Canada entering to the Canada begins at a prominent high level , followed by a dramatical drop to reach the lowest point in April , which reduces to a fifth of the beginning point .
Then the Number remains stable with a slight increase to December .
gold: It shows the number of total vehicles entering Canada during 2017 . It 's clearly possible to see how this value rapidly increase from January until the end of the summer , reaching its maximum value in August . After that , the number of vehicles entering Canada decrease during the last few months of the year .
